    "본문HTML": "<p>\n\n</p><p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\";'><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">안녕하세요</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">?</span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\";'><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">동국대학교 다르마교양교육연구소입니다</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">.</span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\";'><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">저희 연구소에서는 교양교육 전문학술지</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">, </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">『</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">리버럴아츠</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">』 </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">(</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">제</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">5</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">권 </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">호</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">, </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">통권 </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">8</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">호</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">)</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">에 실릴 논문을 아래와 같이 모집합니다</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">.</span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\";'><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">연구자분들의 옥고를 많이 투고해주시기 바랍니다</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">.</span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\";'> </p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\";'> </p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;word-break:keep-all;\";'><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt;\">■ </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt;\">원고 모집 </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt;\">■</span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;word-break:keep-all;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;\";'> </p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\";'><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">1. </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">학술지명</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">: </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">『</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">리버럴아츠</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">』 </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">(KCI </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">등재후보지)</span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\";'> </p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\";'><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">2. </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">논문 모집 분야</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">: </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\">교양교육 관련 전 분야</span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\";'><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">(</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">대학의 교양교육 발전에 의미 있는 이론적 기여를 하거나</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">, </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">인문</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">·</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">사회</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">, </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">이공학</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">, </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">예술</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">·</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">체육</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">, </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">융복합 등 다양한 분야의 교육 현장에서 교양교육을 실천하는 내용 및 방법</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">, </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-size: 11pt;\">교양교육 전반에 대한 이해를 넓힐 수 있는 내용 등</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 11pt;\">)</span></p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\";'> </p>\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"font-size:13.3333px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-tex